			<div class="article-title col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8 pv-sm">
				<h1 class="txt-f4 txt-s7 balance-text">Bougainville’s future: The hard questions</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="article-author pv-md col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6">
															<a class="txt-dn txt-f1 txt-s3 txt-tu" href="/the-interpreter/contributors/articles/oliver-nobetau">
							Oliver Nobetau
						</a>
												</div>
							<div class="article-summary col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10">
					<p class="txt-s5 txt-f1 balance-text txt-lmd">
						There are good reasons to take time before Bougainville cuts loose from PNG.
					</p>
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="article-main-image">
			<img class="article-main-image-img" src="https://www.lowyinstitute.org/sites/default/files/styles/interpreter_article_image/public/2024-05/GettyImages-1184069205.jpg?itok=lKrRGeG9" alt="Bougainville residents queue to vote at a polling station during the independence referendum in Buka, 23 November 2019 (Ness Kerton/AFP via Getty Images)">
              <div class="article-save-btn">
          
        </div>
      							<div class="article-main-image-caption">
					Bougainville residents queue to vote at a polling station during the independence referendum in Buka, 23 November 2019 (Ness Kerton/AFP via Getty Images)
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="clearfix">
			<div class="txt-center pv-md">
				<span class="txt-muted">
					Published 2 May 2024&nbsp;
				</span>

									<ul class="article-tags d-ib list-unstyled">
													<li class="article-tag d-ib">
								<a href="/the-interpreter/archive?issue=203" class="txt-muted txt-dn">
									Pacific Islands
								</a>
							</li>
													<li class="article-tag d-ib">
								<a href="/the-interpreter/archive?issue=381" class="txt-muted txt-dn">
									Bougainville
								</a>
							</li>
													<li class="article-tag d-ib">
								<a href="/the-interpreter/archive?issue=333" class="txt-muted txt-dn">
									Papua New Guinea
								</a>
							</li>
											</ul>
				
								
				
							</div>


			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1"><hr></div>
			</div>

			<div class="row article-body">
				<div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-1">
					<div class="pv-md article-share pin" data-pin data-bounds=".article-body">
            <ul class="list-unstyled clearfix">
